<template>
    <el-card>
        <el-table :data="tableData" stripe style="width: 100%;align-content: center">
            <el-table-column prop="id" label="ID" width="80" />
            <el-table-column prop="cateName" label="题目类型" width="180" />
        </el-table>
    </el-card>
</template>

<script setup>
import {ref} from 'vue';
import axios from '@/util/axios';
const tableData = ref([]);
const initList = async () => {
    const res = await axios.get('/api/survey-cate/all');
    console.log(res)
    tableData.value = res.data.data.surveyCates;
}
initList();
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

</style>
